{"tid":1704162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬧交師係時候諗定聽朝點同班港豬鬧交","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T16:27:38.000Z","uid":206668,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"528fedf50058c6eee652df0a0c54253a5da6a73a","tid":1704162,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"鬧交並唔係為咗真係同佢哋嘈 純粹係加強我哋拖延時間同塞嘅效果<br />\n如果係黨鐵更有用 邊鬧邊塞<br />\n<br />\n你班廢青咁樣做到人就唔啱！<br />\n係時候諗下點駁"},{"pid":"fcdccbffc01e879586008d6e4b095de4ca43b3ca","tid":1704162,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"黎啦"},{"pid":"9cfdf6a95674dece96a75de94489f8b89452b3be","tid":1704162,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"鬧交"},{"pid":"1825c730639cc5e6125fe21ab8fbc78af259f5db","tid":1704162,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先58%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=068d203f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=4899f5aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af316d78e6fa955112aca2ab1ac5e2db17ba3e85","tid":1704162,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母<br />\n阻9交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出泥<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雙十一，周圍塞，阻塞交通變相全民罷工 悼念完一定要有行動，手足既血不可白流<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 扮工師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【召集和理非】聽朝7點唔知點做好？入嚟睇下有咩最簡單嘅嘢可以做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽日可能出現嘅情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703148</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」聽日需要大量無裝備嘅路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n驅逐共黨 光復香港"},{"pid":"b31568f6dfb3bcd5f5a16a558bf2098ca439b084","tid":1704162,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://debate.fandom.com/zh-hk/wiki/%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96%E8